---
title: "update-api-contracts-docs — resolve area → preflight → re-audit → merge → confirm → write → report"
---
%%{init: {'theme': 'neutral'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Claude
    participant FS as File System
    participant PM as protocol-mapper subagent

    User->>Claude: /update-api-contracts-docs <area> [path]

    note over Claude: Capture timestamps

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Preflight — resolve area argument
    Claude->>FS: Check api-contracts-analysis.json and .claude/docs/
    FS-->>Claude: known boundaries + existing docs
    alt area is predefined axis (http/auth/realtime/errors/all)
        Claude->>FS: Require reference-api-contracts.md + JSON
    else area matches boundary ID in JSON
        Claude->>FS: Read JSON for boundary descriptor
    else area matches doc file in .claude/docs/
        Claude->>FS: Read .claude/docs/<area>.md
        FS-->>Claude: doc content — identify boundary from it
    else nothing resolves
        Claude->>User: Unknown area. Known boundaries: [...] Known docs: [...]
        break Skill aborts
            Claude->>User: Clarify and retry
        end
    end

    note over Claude,PM: Phase: Re-audit
    Claude->>PM: protocol-mapper with boundary descriptor<br/>+ project roots from JSON (or detect if absent)
    PM-->>Claude: updated findings for this boundary

    note over Claude: Phase: Merge
    Claude->>FS: Read target doc
    FS-->>Claude: current content
    Claude->>Claude: Replace only changed section(s)<br/>Preserve all other content verbatim
    opt companion diagram exists (api-<boundary-id>.mmd)
        Claude->>Claude: Prepare diagram diff
    end
    opt api-contracts-analysis.json exists
        Claude->>Claude: Patch matching boundary entry in JSON
    end

    note over Claude,User: Phase: User confirmation
    Claude->>User: Diff for <area>:<br/>[before] vs [after]<br/>[1] Accept [2] Accept all [3] Abort
    User-->>Claude: choice
    alt abort
        break Skill aborts — no writes
            Claude->>User: Aborted
        end
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Write
    Claude->>FS: Write updated doc
    FS-->>Claude: OK
    opt diagram updated
        Claude->>FS: Write .claude/sequences/api-<boundary-id>.mmd
        FS-->>Claude: OK
    end
    opt JSON patched
        Claude->>FS: Write api-contracts-analysis.json
        FS-->>Claude: OK
    end

    note over Claude,FS: Phase: Report
    Claude->>FS: Write .claude/state/reports/update-api-contracts-docs-<ts>.md
    FS-->>Claude: OK
    Claude->>User: Updated: <area> refreshed in <doc-path><br/>Changes: N sections · M lines
